auer RC, editors. <span class="ref-journal">Minerals in soil environments, Soil Science Society of America book series. 2nd ed.</span> Madison, Wisconsin: Soil Science Society of America; 1989. pp. 913\xe2\x80\x93974. <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Minerals+in+soil+environments,+Soil+Science+Society+of+America+book+series.+2nd+ed&amp;author=LR+Drees&amp;author=LP+Wilding&amp;author=NE+Smeck&amp;author=AL+Senkagi&amp;publication_year=1989&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1435987&amp;issue-id=130620&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="ppat-0020032-b023"><span class="element-citation">Chipera SJ, Bish DL. Baseline studies of the Clay Minerals Society source clays: Powder X-ray diffraction analyses. <span><span class="ref-journal">Clays Clay Miner. </span>2001;<span class="ref-vol">49</span>:398\xe2\x80\x93409.</span> <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Clays+Clay+Miner&amp;title=Baseline+studies+of+the+Clay+Minerals+Society+source+clays:+Powder+X-ray+diffraction+analyses&amp;author=SJ+Chipera&amp;author=DL+Bish&amp;volume=49&amp;publication_year=2001&amp;pages=398-409&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1435987&amp;issue-id=130620&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="ppat-0020032-b024"><span class="element-citation">Jackson ML.  <span class="ref-journal">Soil chemical analysis. Revised 2nd Ed.</span> Madison, Wisconsin: Parallel Press; 2005.  <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Soil+chemical+analysis.+Revised+2nd+Ed&amp;author=ML+Jackson&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1435987&amp;issue-id=130620&amp;journal-id=349&amp;F